com.jdbwc.core
Class MySQLDatabaseMetaData

java.lang.Object
  com.jdbwc.core.MySQLDBMDFromInfoSchema
      com.jdbwc.core.MySQLDatabaseMetaData
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.sql.DatabaseMetaData, java.sql.Wrapper
public class MySQLDatabaseMetaData
extends MySQLDBMDFromInfoSchema
implements java.sql.DatabaseMetaData

This MetaData class is designed for MySql implementations.

This implementation has had its query logic migrated to a separate class MySQLDbMetaDataFromInfoSchema.

NOTE: Portions of this class were derived from MySql-Connector/J. Namely the (Strings) function names, (Strings) keywords and a few basic methods (most derived methods have been altered from the original Connector/J release, the key names and words are unchanged).

Version:
1.0.0.0
Author:
Tim Gall (Oz-DevWorX)
